{"Id":583905,"Title":"万氏四忠三节诗五章","Dynasty":"明","Author":"霍韬","Context":"山高棱棱，石叠棱棱。储时元精，濠虹大横。元精虹横，泄丛勇贞。彼勇且贞，濠虹之乡。佐时真人，佛时天纲。恢恢猷烈，赫赫鼎常。殒身殉贞，四有休耿光。耿光则那，祖考厥孙子。孙子忠勋，考祖是似。于戏，不间厥心，以绵尔祉。四祖忠勋，曰阳德则刚。女妇之德，柔则其常。懿其万母，烈节冷霜。冷霜凄冬，三叶同芳。北背之柏，茕矣朝阳。于戏，烈节不忘。懿彼烈节，犹曰妇人。誇彼丈夫，乃有失厥身。天畀德于人，勇得其纯。乃身失矣，曾不惭妇之仁。渭氏作歌，以勖自新。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"9a35a873e48c3735e395eac6c18fa239","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7161576,"Sentence":"懿彼烈节，犹曰妇人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yì bi liè jiē ，yóu yuē fù rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161560,"Sentence":"山高棱棱，石叠棱棱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shān gāo lēng lēng ，dàn dié lēng lēng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161561,"Sentence":"储时元精，濠虹大横。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chǔ shǐ yuán jīng ，háo hóng dà héng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161562,"Sentence":"元精虹横，泄丛勇贞。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yuán jīng hóng héng ，xiè cóng yǒng zhēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161563,"Sentence":"彼勇且贞，濠虹之乡。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bi yǒng jū zhēn ，háo hóng zhī xiāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161564,"Sentence":"佐时真人，佛时天纲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zuǒ shǐ zhēn rén ，fó shǐ tiān gāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161565,"Sentence":"恢恢猷烈，赫赫鼎常。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huī huī yóu liè ，hè hè ding cháng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161566,"Sentence":"殒身殉贞，四有休耿光。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǔn shēn xùn zhēn ，sì yǒu xīu gěng guāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161567,"Sentence":"耿光则那，祖考厥孙子。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gěng guāng zé nā ，zǔ kǎo jué sūn zi "